text: Schönebeck-Felgeleben station is a railway station in the Felgeleben district in the municipality of Schönebeck (Elbe), located in the Salzlandkreis district in Saxony-Anhalt, Germany. ==References== Category:Railway stations in Saxony-Anhalt Category:Buildings and structures in Salzlandkreis
title: Schönebeck-Felgeleben station
